name: Theia
description: "The Titaness of sight and by extension the goddess who endowed gold, silver and gems with their brilliance and intrinsic value” // Emphasis is placed on abstract uniformity through various hidden light sources, interwoven three-dimensional pieces, and seemingly uncontrollable displacements.  A study of particle systems, multi-layered refractions, and interacting luminance layers // 2563 × 3204 px
